[p 
	[em 
		"Antarctic Adventure
	]em
	" was released by Konami in 1983 for the MSX and was later ported to other platforms. You play as Penta, a penguin racing around Antarctica to different research stations while avoiding sea lions, breaks in the ice, and a time limit. The game was popular enough that it spawned a sequel, 
	[a href=/2199M 
		"Penguin Adventure
	]a
	", and Penta became Konami's mascot for a time.
